MsgData.Message: Nice to meet you!
Let's go together!
It's an honor to meet you!
I will do my best to make it a pleasant journey.
Please, use my powers to your liking.

We did it!

Come on, let's go!
Finally!
Enemy sighted!
There's an enemy there!
There! Careful!
That enemy is disgusting...
A formidable foe! Stay vigilant!
Thank you!
Help me, quickly!
Please help me!
I...I messed up!
Ugh...my strength!
Negligence is forbidden!
Come on, let's do this!
Defeated!
This is our victory!
Looks like we survived.
Do it now, Arisen!

This can't be!
Like this!
I'm recovering.

Over here!

necessary.

step

Where shall I accompany you today?
Yes, what is it?
What's wrong, Ser Arisen?
Master, I am with you!

The other day, I was invited by another Arisen to

I'll come to you, please wait!

Good luck!
